Here is a list of features currently available in [Libravatar](https://www.libravatar.org) and how it differs from [Gravatar](http://www.gravatar.com).

[[!table class="border" data="""
                                  | Libravatar                                           | Gravatar
JPEG and **PNG** support          | Yes                                                  | Yes
GIF support                       | Yes                                                  | No
