**HTTPS** support                 | Yes                                                  | Yes
**IPv6** support                  | Yes                                                  | &mdash;
Supported email hashes            | MD5 and **SHA256**                                   | [MD5 only](http://en.gravatar.com/site/faq/#answer-2-1)
**OpenID** URL support            | Yes                                                  | &mdash;
Redirection to Gravatar           | Yes                                                  | Not needed :)
Customizable default image        | Yes                                                  | Yes
MPAA-style image ratings          | G-rated only                                         | Yes
Text-based profile information    | &mdash;                                              | Yes
**Federation** via DNS SRV records| Yes                                                  | &mdash;
**LDAP** authentication           | Yes                                                  | &mdash;
**OpenID** authentication         | Yes                                                  | &mdash;
Automatic photo **importers**     | [[Yes|photo importers]]                              | &mdash;
Translated user interface         | No                                                   | [Yes](http://en.gravatar.com/site/translations/)
